ed artillery]]\n|160\n|Fitted on 6x6 Mercedes-Benz Zetros vehicle<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.defenceweb.co.za/index.php?option=com_content&view=article&id=48532|title=Algeria locally modifying artillery {{!}} defenceWeb|last=Martin|first=Guy|website=www.defenceweb.co.za|language=en-gb|access-date=2018-04-04}}</ref>\n|- style=\"background:#efefef; color:black\"\n\n|- style=\"background:#efefef; color:black\"\n|[[WAC-21]]\n|{{flag|China}}\n|18<ref name=\"auto2\">{{Cite news|url=https://www.menadefense.net/2017/07/31/lexercice-majd-2017-explique-images/|title=L'exercice Majd 2017 expliqu\u00e9 en images - MENADEFENSE|date=2017-07-31|work=MENADEFENSE|access-date=2018-04-04|language=fr-FR}}</ref>\n|\n|-\n|[[160mm Mortar M1943]]\n| rowspan=\"2\" |{{flag|Soviet Union}}\n| rowspan=\"3\" |[[Mortar (weapon)|Mortar]]\n|60\n|\n|- style=\"background:#efefef; color:black\"\n|[[120-PM-43 mortar]]\n|120\n|\n|-\n|[[W86 120mm mortar]]\n|{{flag|China}}\n|60<ref name=\"auto2\"/>\n|\n|}\n\n=== MRLs ===\n{| style=\"width:90%;\"\n|- style=\"background:#aabccc;\"\n! style=\"width:15%;\"|Model\n!'''Origin'''\n! style=\"width:15%;\"|Type\n! style=\"width:10%;\"|Quantity\n! style=\"width:50%;\"|Notes\n|- style=\"background:#efefef; color:black\"\n| [[BM-21 Grad]] \n| rowspan=\"2\" | {{flag|Soviet Union}} \n|\n|48\n|\n|-\n| [[BM-24]] \n| \n| 48\n|\n|\n|- \n| [[BM-14]] \n|\n| \n|48<ref>Military Balance 2016, p. 393.</ref> \n|- \n| [[BM-30 Smerch]] \n|\n| \n|50<ref name=\"IISS2015\" /> \n|- style=\"background:#efefef; color:black\"\n| [[TOS-1]]A \n|{{flag|Russia}}|| ||52<ref>{{cite web|url=https://xn--b1aga5aadd.xn--p1ai/2017/%D0%A4%D0%BE%D1%80%D1%83%D0%BC%D0%90%D1%80%D0%BC%D0%B8%D1%8F313/|title=\u0410\u043b\u0436\u0438\u0440 \u0437\u0430\u043a\u0443\u043f\u0438\u043b \u0443 \u0420\u043e\u0441\u0441\u0438\u0438 \u0422\u041e\u0421-1\u0410 \"\u0421\u043e\u043b\u043d\u0446\u0435\u043f\u0435\u043a\"|website=\u0412\u043e\u0435\u043d\u043d\u043e\u0435.\u0420\u0424|access-date=2018-01-23}}</ref><ref