/B077YS7M2H |title=Famous in Love: Amazon Prime Video |publisher=Amazon |date=April 5, 2018 |access-date=April 13, 2018}}</ref>\n\nIn Spain, it airs exclusively on [[:es:HBO Espa\u00f1a|HBO Spain]] with new episodes every Thursday.<ref>{{cite web |url=https://losreyesdelmando.com/2018/04/05/famous-in-love-regresa-a-hbo-espana-con-su-segunda-temporada/ |title=\"Famous in Love\" regresa a HBO Espa\u00f1a con su segunda temporada |language=Spanish |date=April 8, 2018 |access-date=May 11, 2018}}</ref>\n\n== Ratings ==\n{{Television season ratings\n| hide_timeslot     = y\n| hide_tv_season    = y\n| hide_rank         = y\n| hide_18_49_rating = y\n\n| link1             = #Season 1 (2017)\n| episodes1         = 10<!-- should reflect the number of episodes that contribute to the average given in the last column -->\n| start1            = {{Start date|2017|4|18}}\n| end1              = {{End date|2017|6|13}}\n| startrating1         = 0.65<ref name=\"1.01\" />\n| endrating1           = 0.23<ref name=\"1.09\" />\n| viewers1          = {{decimals|{{#expr:((\n                      0.653 + <!-- raw ratings data from Episode 1 -->\n                      0.389 + <!-- raw ratings data from Episode 2 -->\n                      0.299 + <!-- raw ratings data from Episode 3 -->\n                      0.282 + <!-- raw ratings data from Episode 4 -->\n                      0.212 + <!-- raw ratings data from Episode 5 -->\n                      0.258 + <!-- raw ratings data from Episode 6 -->\n                      0.288 + <!-- raw ratings data from Episode 7 -->\n                      0.334 + <!-- raw ratings data from Episode 8 -->\n                      0.360 + <!-- raw ratings data from Episode 9 -->\n                      0.230   <!-- raw ratings data from Episode 10 -->\n                              <!-- end of raw data; please make sure one plus sign (+) follows every number above except the last entry -->\n                      )/ 10   <!-- number of episodes in this calculation; 