T, and those substantially less than 100 words are most likely to be scrutinized for possible copyright violation. -->\n| LineColor       = 40E0D0\n}}\n}}\n\n== Broadcast ==\nThe second season returned with a two-hour premiere on Freeform on April 4, 2018.<ref>{{cite press release |url=http://www.thefutoncritic.com/news/2018/01/18/breaking-news-from-freeforms-first-ever-freeform-summit-870212/20180118freeform02/ |title=Breaking News from Freeform's First-Ever Freeform Summit |publisher=Freeform |via=The Futon Critic |date=January 18, 2018 |access-date=March 14, 2018}}</ref> It aired in Canada on [[E! (Canadian TV channel)|E!]] on April 8, 2018, with new episodes set to air every Sunday.<ref>{{cite video |url=http://www.eonline.com/ca/videos/272578/famous-in-love-returns-april-8 |title=Famous In Love Returns to E! |publisher=E! |date=April 5, 2018 |access-date=April 6, 2018}}</ref>\n\nIn the United Kingdom, it airs exclusively on [[Amazon Prime Video]] with new episodes every Thursday.<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.amazon.co.uk/gp/video/detail/B077YS7M2H |title=Famous in Love: Amazon Prime Video |publisher=Amazon |date=April 5, 2018 |access-date=April 13, 2018}}</ref>\n\nIn Spain, it airs exclusively on [[:es:HBO Espa\u00f1a|HBO Spain]] with new episodes every Thursday.<ref>{{cite web |url=https://losreyesdelmando.com/2018/04/05/famous-in-love-regresa-a-hbo-espana-con-su-segunda-temporada/ |title=\"Famous in Love\" regresa a HBO Espa\u00f1a con su segunda temporada |language=Spanish |date=April 8, 2018 |access-date=May 11, 2018}}</ref>\n\n== Ratings ==\n{{Television season ratings\n| hide_timeslot     = y\n| hide_tv_season    = y\n| hide_rank         = y\n| hide_18_49_rating = y\n\n| link1             = #Season 1 (2017)\n| episodes1         = 10<!-- should reflect the number of episodes that contribute to the average given in the last column -->\n| start1            = {{Start date|2017|4|18}}\n| end1              = {{End date|2017|6|13}}\n| startrating1         = 0