ion for as many as 243 Indonesians\u2014to be quarantined in [[Natuna Regency]] for 14 days\u2014was scheduled for 1 February 2020 and to take around 9 hours.<ref name=liputan64168925>{{Cite web |url=https://www.liputan6.com/news/read/4168925/wni-dari-wuhan-akan-dikarantina-14-hari-di-natuna |title=WNI dari Wuhan Akan Dikarantina 14 Hari di Natuna |first=Delvira |last=Hutabarat |date=1 February 2020 |website=Liputan6.com |language=id |access-date=1 February 2020 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200201064919/https://www.liputan6.com/news/read/4168925/wni-dari-wuhan-akan-dikarantina-14-hari-di-natuna |archive-date=1 February 2020 |url-status=live }}</ref> The [[Government of Indonesia|Indonesian government]] chartered an [[Airbus A330#A330-300|A330-300]]CEO (PK-LDY), [[Lion Air]] Group's [[Batik Air]] aircraft with identified flight number ID-8619 (18 crews and 30 medics) to evacuate around 200 Indonesian citizens from Hubei, including Wuhan City.<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://pressrelease.kontan.co.id/release/informasi-terkini-operasional-batik-air-misi-kemanusiaan-penerbangan-id-8619-rute-wuhan-ke-batam|title=Informasi Terkini Operasional Batik Air Misi Kemanusiaan Penerbangan ID-8619 Rute Wuhan ke Batam|website=pressrelease.id|access-date=3 February 2020|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200203134114/https://pressrelease.kontan.co.id/release/informasi-terkini-operasional-batik-air-misi-kemanusiaan-penerbangan-id-8619-rute-wuhan-ke-batam|archive-date=3 February 2020|url-status=live}}</ref><ref name=tempo1302112>{{Cite web |url=https://en.tempo.co/read/1302112/batik-air-chartered-to-evacuate-indonesian-citizens-from-wuhan |title=Batik Air Chartered to Evacuate Indonesian Citizens from Wuhan |last=Murti |first=Markus Wisnu |date=31 January 2020 |website=Tempo |access-date=1 February 2020 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200131192450/https://en.tempo.co/read/1302112/batik-air-chartered-to-evacuate-indonesian-citizens-from-wuhan |archive-date=31